Launch Ec2 Instance.
connect ec2 instance from terminal.
Install Java 8 - sudo yum install java-1.8.0-openjdk-devel .
sudo /usr/sbin/alternatives --config java
choose option 2.
sudo /usr/sbin/alternatives --config javac
choose option 1.
Go to AWS console and right click on ec2 instant and image->create image. 
Give name and hit create.
